Cannabis oil is the preparation form receiving more attention recently (
 Pacifici et al., 2017; 
 Carcieri et al., 2018; 
 MacCallum and Russo, 2018; 
 Pacifici et al., 2018; 
 Bettiol et al., 2019; 
 Deidda et al., 2019; 
 Mudge and Brown, 2019; 
 Pacifici et al., 2019; 
 Pegoraro et al., 2019) due to its easy adjustment of the needed individual administration dose along the treatment period, together with the enhanced bioavailability of its active compounds.
